<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="15Sep1917"><font color="red">15 September 1917</font>, <cite>BLHW</cite> (Nora Joyce to Harriet Weaver): My husband is now at home again but will be convalescent for two or three weeks still. The operation was satisfactory &hellip; He was very glad indeed to hear the good news in your letter and thanks you for your kind and generous patronage of his <cite>Ulysses</cite>. </div>
